@section MapiClient Calling Arguments
@example
MapiClient [ options ]
@end example
Options are:
@table @code
@item  -b t/f      
@item  --blocked=true/false 
	Run the interaction in blocked transfer mode

@item -D          @item --dump           
dump sql database 
@item -e          @item --error          
exit on error 
@item -H          @item --history        
load/save cmdline history (default off) 
@item -h hostname @item --host=hostname  
host to connect to 
@item -i          @item --interactive    
read stdin after command line args 
@item  -l language @item --language=lang  
@verb{ { }mal,sql,mil,xquery @verb{ } } 
@item  -P passwd   @item --passwd=passwd  
password 
@item  -p portnr   @item --port=portnr    
port to connect to 
@item  -q          @item --quiet          
don't print welcome message 
@item  -s stmt     @item --statement=stmt 
run single statement 
@item  -T          @item --time           
time commands 
@item  -t          @item --trace          
trace Monet interaction 
@item  -u user     @item --user=user      
user id 
@item  -?          @item --help           
show this usage message 
@end table
